{"tid":614412,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個見過最核突經歷","createTime":"2018-04-02T13:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T15:59:45.000Z","uid":52023,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"999258f4084c38223a9460c4abfaaf4acb374245","tid":614412,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T13:33:34.000Z","msg":"有一次喺街市附緊等人 落緊好大雨<br />\n街市門口就有一條十幾級樓梯<br />\n有個師奶就成腳濕哂咁行緊上去 後面就有個西裝友跟住<br />\n<br />\n個師奶就著緊嗰啲flapflap吓但係又裝到水嘅婆仔鞋<br />\n落咁大雨實好多水<br />\n咁啱佢上樓嗰吓就flect咗一條水花出嚟 <br />\n好似洗頭水廣告fing頭髮嗰啲水花咁<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>一嘢成條水花flect咗入西裝友個口度</strong></span><br />\n啲水仲要係唔撚同色<br />\n師奶行前面梗係咩都唔知 西裝又好似唔知啲水係喺隻鞋度飛入去咁淨係吐咗一兩淡<br />\n成個過程得我睇到<br />\n<br />\n嗰吓我睇到即刻唔敢再望 <br />\n成世人都有陰影<br />\n而家每次落雨都唔敢行樓梯<br />\n好撚想嘔"},{"pid":"4776d1f41636095c1ffdb453763c33ac312f6952","tid":614412,"uid":177656,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T13:37:41.000Z","msg":"個西裝友係咪弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f949103dca7b6e4c2d6920036d7aa7bf1d329e60","tid":614412,"uid":61766,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T13:54:18.000Z","msg":"公司女廁得兩格<br />\n入到去<br />\n第一格就廁所水湧哂出黎，成地都水浸<br />\n第二格就有條屎係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66eedb0152abc6f124f38f794dc8122c653e1214","tid":614412,"uid":52023,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4776d1f41636095c1ffdb453763c33ac312f6952","tid":614412,"uid":177656,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T13:37:41.000Z","msg":"個西裝友係咪弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T14:14:21.000Z","msg":"佢應該以為啲遮滴出嚟掛<br />\n得我見到成件事過程 <br />\n好大陰影"},{"pid":"a862a2f1aaa7353a050c01afe013723c341766a1","tid":614412,"uid":172150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T14:16:40.000Z","msg":"見過老母掛住睇電視<br />\n咁啱有隻烏蠅停咗喺佢準備放入口嘅豬紅到<br />\n然後佢放咗落口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f8db21a70548c2c4af78901a1224e672e569e9","tid":614412,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T14:36:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e411d649a6ab3fc6c967b781fbcf07ddbebdd00","tid":614412,"uid":44263,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T15:45:09.000Z","msg":"呀婆瀨咗屎成褲成床都係<br />\n幫佢除褲清潔時呀婆對腳夾實唔肯鬆開<br />\n我用手踭加前手臂頂實呀婆其中一隻腳另一隻手去清潔<br />\n然後我成條手臂都係呀婆啲水屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n洗咗三次手臂都仲覺得有種濕濕滑滑"},{"pid":"52a86d1d06397e918e117297702def18325348b6","tid":614412,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e411d649a6ab3fc6c967b781fbcf07ddbebdd00","tid":614412,"uid":44263,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T15:45:09.000Z","msg":"呀婆瀨咗屎成褲成床都係<br />\n幫佢除褲清潔時呀婆對腳夾實唔肯鬆開<br />\n我用手踭加前手臂頂實呀婆其中一隻腳另一隻手去清潔<br />\n然後我成條手臂都係呀婆啲水屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n洗咗三次手臂都仲覺得有種濕濕滑滑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T15:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97812fa31d29f8c7d1735e8ebe14c6c477889a2f","tid":614412,"uid":177924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6e411d649a6ab3fc6c967b781fbcf07ddbebdd00","tid":614412,"uid":44263,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T15:45:09.000Z","msg":"呀婆瀨咗屎成褲成床都係<br />\n幫佢除褲清潔時呀婆對腳夾實唔肯鬆開<br />\n我用手踭加前手臂頂實呀婆其中一隻腳另一隻手去清潔<br />\n然後我成條手臂都係呀婆啲水屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n洗咗三次手臂都仲覺得有種濕濕滑滑"},"citedBy"